rows.name:
I don't think I've ever seen your equal, kid, even among
the elites of the distant future.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070306_MSG0003
rows.name: All right, repairs are done. I'm headed back to the city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070306_MSG0004
rows.name:
I've got to get back to developing new products
and extracting lucre from the population.
Past, present, or future, time is money![ST:wait ]
